director.name: 吉多·范德韦弗 Guido van der Werve

this_title: Nummer twee, just because I’m standing here doesn’t mean I want to
introduction: Standing on a suburban street, the artist slowly walks backwards until he is hit by a car. A blue police van stops. Five young dancers emerge and dance Arcangelo Corelli’s Concerto grosso per la notte di Natale in front of the artist’s inert body.源自：https://www.schermodellarte.org/en/film/nummer-twee-just-because-im-standing-here-doesnt-mean-i-want-to/
